accessibility.text: We emerge onto the main theatre stage, an incredible shot combining old and new. And the lights go out…
Rosa opens the massive doorways and is in awe of the baroque interior foyer of this classical Parisian Theatre.
Rosa brings us through the foyer and let’s us into a ‘VIPs only’ space — the doors to the inner areas behind the stage
